de-body and narrow-body aircrafts, in addition to leasing new ones to ensure stronger connectivity for journeys to global destinations and international events. With our flights, travellers can also expect crew members to converse in Indian languages, allowing seamless and easy conversations to make your journey memorable. </p> <br /> <p>\n\nAir India is one of the premier airlines, with a network spanning across USA, Canada, UK, Europe, Far East, south-east Asia, Australia and the Gulf. Being a Star Alliance member, travelers can access 26 foreign airlines loyalty programmes that are linked with ours.\nThe connection between the culturally rich city of Amritsar and cosmopolitan Birmingham is not just a great trip but also a meaningful journey.  </p>','Experience the best of Birmingham','Embark on an unforgettable trip to Birmingham with Air India and explore a world of culture, adventure, or simply a unique experience that the Venice of UK has to offer. ','Air India offers outstanding services for Indian travellers','\n   <h2 className=\"font-[Montserrat] leading-10 font-semibold text-[#585B5C] text-center text-[41px] pb-5 mb-[20px] sms:text-[24px] sms:leading-8\">\n   Air India offers<br /> outstanding services for Indian travellers\n            </h2>','Airport Information','2022-11-04 13:33:35.900000','2022-11-14 10:02:05.265000','2022-11-10 11:47:39.659000',9,10,'The Birmingham Airport offers services like ','Amritsar','atq','Birmingham','bhx','Birmingham is one of the most popular tourist destinations in England. There are numerous historical places & monuments, picturesque canals, museums, parks & gardens, shopping centres, walking tours and fun activities spread across the city. With many international sporting and cultural events happening in the city, one can immerse themselves into the city’s offerings.\nThe Transport for West Midlands is in charge of organising the local public transportation system in Birmingham. Because of the city’s central location in England, Birmingham serves as a significant transportation hub for the highways, rails, and canal networks – tourists can travel through the city in easily available cabs, buses, trams, and canals. ','Key services offered at Amritsar Airport','<span>You can book tickets with Air India for your trip to Birmingham and decide what adventures you want to have there. Plan your trip to Birmingham by visiting </span><a  style=\"color:#486AAE\"  href=\"https://visitbirmingham.com/\">https://visitbirmingham.com/</a> \n','IN',NULL),(25,'ongoing promotion','jfk-bom','Connecting New York to Mumbai','Flying Air India','<p>To meet the demands of travellers looking to travel to India, Air India will start operating daily flights from JFK International Airport in New York, USA, to Mumbai, India. Thanks to the introduction of the new airline route, people now have a terrific option for travelling to Mumbai and enjoying everything the city has to offer. With our one-of-a-kind nonstop flight from JFK International Airport in New York to Mumbai, you will have an excellent travel experience that is viable and comfortable.</p>\n\n<p>This is a result of Air India\'s systematic and objective plan to meet the needs of visitors to India and recapture the top spot in the international aviation market. Air India now operates two daily flights from JFK airport, thus enhancing its status as a top international airline provider with 47 weekly and 7 daily flights between the US and India. With its most recent effort to link New York City with India, Air India now operates 21 weekly flights between Mumbai and the two airports in New York City—JFK International Airport and Newark Liberty International Airport—offering a variety of travel opportunities to interested travellers.</p>\n\n<p>We at Air India understand the demands of Indian travellers, whether they are flying for business or pleasure. The flight from New York’s JFK International Airport to Mumbai has the potential to be the perfect start to an exciting journey to India.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n','Experience the best of Mumbai','It is a pleasure to visit Mumbai with our services and take in all of its top attractions. By choosing our quick and effective service, you may fly to the city and enjoy all that Mumbai has to offer its visitors. Tourists looking for culture, excitement, or simply a unique experience will discover that the city has a lot to offer. You\'ll create lifelong memories when you visit the city.','Air India offers outstanding services for Indian travellers','   <h2 className=\"font-[Montserrat] leading-10 font-semibold text-[#585B5C] text-center text-[41px] pb-5 mb-[20px] sms:text-[24px] sms:leading-8\">\n   Air India offers<br /> outstanding services for Indian travellers\n            </h2>','Airport Information','2022-11-16 06:07:04.383000','2022-11-16 10:49:24.783000','2022-11-16 10:49:24.777000',9,9,'The Mumbai airport offers services like','New York','jfk','Mumbai','bom','One of India\'s largest and most populated cities in India is Mumbai. The city is famous as India\'s entertainment and financial capital where the population is renowned for its intense vigour and active lifestyle. The colonial architecture in Mumbai\'s central area is some of the best and most elegant in India yet if you explore some of the city\'s more obscure lanes, you will also find a variety of bazaars, temples, upmarket cafés, bustling beaches and extremely stunning nightlife. Around every corner in Mumbai, there is something to impress you. In this metropolis, there is a little something for everyone.','The John F. Kennedy International Airport offers services like','<span>For your journey to Mumbai, choose Air India for an amazing flying experience. We help you make the best start to your visit to India. Prepare for your trip to Mumbai by visiting </span><a   style=\"color:#486AAE\" href=\"https://www.maharashtratourism.gov.in/\">https://www.maharashtratourism.gov.in/.</a>','US',NULL),(26,'ongoing promotion','bom-jfk','Direct flights from Mumbai to New York','Flying Air India','<p>Air India is starting flying daily flights from Mumbai, India, to JFK International Airport, New York, USA, to accommodate the needs of Indian tourists. Indian travellers now have a fantastic choice for visiting New York and taking advantage of everything that the city has to offer thanks to the introduction of the new airline route. You will have a great travelling experience that is both convenient and comfortable with our one-of-a-kind nonstop flight linking Mumbai to JFK International Airport in New York.</p> <br> <p>\n\nThis is a part of Air India\'s systematic strategy to satisfy the needs of Indian travellers while reclaiming the top rank in the global aviation industry. This route has increased Air India’s presence at JKF airport to two daily flights, further strengthening Air India’s reputation as a premiere international flight option with 47 weekly flights and 7 daily flights to the US. With its latest attempt to connect India to the big apple, Air India now has 21 weekly flights from Mumbai to the two airports of New York, JFK International Airport and the Newark Liberty International Airport.\n </p> <br> <p>\nWhether on vacation or flying for business, we are aware of the needs of Indian tourists. The travel from Mumbai to New York has the potential to be the ideal beginning of an enlightening journey. Information on the flight between Mumbai and JFK International Airport may be found in the table below. </p>','Experience the best of New York','You can travel to New York to explore and take in everything the city has to offer its visitors with the help of our trustworthy and well-respected services. Whether you\'re looking for culture, adventure, or a one-of-a-kind experience, the city has it all. Make the most of your trip by ensuring that it is unforgettable with our premiere flying experience.  \n','Air India offers outstanding services for Indian travellers','\n   <h2 class